**Organization**: Global Manufacturing & Technology Conglomerate
- **Revenue**: $50B annually
- **Employees**: 500,000+ worldwide
- **Facilities**: 200+ manufacturing and R&D centers
- **Markets**: 150+ countries
- **Products**: Advanced materials, electronics, pharmaceuticals, aerospace

**Challenge**: Traditional computing systems unable to handle complex optimization problems at scale, limiting competitive advantage and operational efficiency.

